**Using curl:**

```bash
# Test GET endpoint
curl http://localhost:8000/api/{{ endpoint_path | default("items") }}/

# Test POST endpoint
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/{{ endpoint_path | default("items") }}/ \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"name": "Test Item"}'
```

**Using httpie (recommended):**

```bash
# Install httpie
